18
00:00:47,192 --> 00:00:49,952
President! I'm sorry.

19
00:00:51,122 --> 00:00:52,922
Burn in everlasting fire.

20
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:54,652
I'll catch up with you later.

21
00:00:58,752 --> 00:00:59,752
Boss!

22
00:00:59,822 --> 00:01:00,922
