23
00:01:01,422 --> 00:01:02,922
Boss, stop.

24
00:01:03,552 --> 00:01:05,652
Mr Bong, are you all right?

25
00:01:06,652 --> 00:01:07,952
What are you doing?

26
00:01:08,022 --> 00:01:09,122
Boss.

27
00:01:10,222 --> 00:01:11,422
Don't do this.

28
00:01:12,292 --> 00:01:13,952
- Move. - No matter what...

29
00:01:14,862 --> 00:01:16,422
Mr Bong did,

30
