Well, what is it?

811
00:41:06,322 --> 00:41:08,192
Were you the one who kicked out...

812
00:41:08,262 --> 00:41:09,322
Sung Min's dad?

813
00:41:11,952 --> 00:41:13,192
What are you talking about?

814
00:41:13,822 --> 00:41:15,322
Why would I do that?

815
00:41:16,352 --> 00:41:17,652
Let me rephrase that.

816
00:41:18,522 --> 00:41:20,452
Did you do something to Sung Min?

817
00:41:23,762 --> 00:41:25,452
Did he say something?

818
00:41:25,922 --> 00:41:28,052
Did he say that I did something wrong to him?

819
00:41:28,152 --> 00:41:30,652
No, I'm asking you because he won't tell me.

820
00:41:31,822 --> 00:41:34,152
There's something for sure, but he won't tell me.

821
00:41:35,852 --> 00:41:36,922
He's avoiding me.

822
00:41:39,322 --> 00:41:41,552
Hyun Ji, I didn't do anything.

823
00:41:41,922 --> 00:41:43,552
Really? Can I trust you?

824
00:41:43,652 --> 00:41:44,762
Of course.

825
00:41:46,052 --> 00:41:47,122
Dad.

826
00:41:47,422 --> 00:41:50,262
I hope you never disappoint me.

827
00:41:51,762 --> 00:41:53,192
You know what I mean, right?

828
00:41:55,452 --> 00:41:56,852
Of course.

829
00:42:13,152 --> 00:42:16,052
(Stop the redevelopment project, Choongshim Construction)

830
00:42:32,292 --> 00:42:33,292
What are you doing?

831
00:42:35,652 --> 00:42:36,822
Oh.

832
00:42:39,852 --> 00:42:41,452
- What is this? - It's...

833
00:42:42,052 --> 00:42:43,652
It's galbi.

834
00:42:43,822 --> 00:42:45,552
Cook some for your dad.

835
00:42:46,022 --> 00:42:47,192
You should have some, too.

836
00:42:47,262 --> 00:42:48,422
Are you kidding me?

837
00:42:48,852 --> 00:42:50,152
What are you trying to pull?

838
00:42:50,652 --> 00:42:52,822
Do you think you can bribe us with something like this?

839
00:42:53,922 --> 00:42:55,292
You're from that German bar, right?

840
00:42:55,452 --> 00:42:56,952
I guess you finally remembered.

841
00:43:00,122 --> 00:43:01,422
There are no words...

842
00:43:01,952 --> 00:43:03,652
that could express how sorry I am.

843
00:43:03,822 --> 00:43:05,222
Are you going to be me for forgiveness?

844
00:43:09,652 --> 00:43:11,322
What happened...

845
00:43:11,822 --> 00:43:13,292
to your dad?

846
00:43:13,322 --> 00:43:15,852
After what happened to our store, he fell ill from the shock.

847
00:43:16,422 --> 00:43:18,022
You gangsters...

848
00:43:18,052 --> 00:43:19,922
broke my family apart.

849
00:43:29,262 --> 00:43:30,262
By the way,

850
00:43:31,022 --> 00:43:32,222
what did Choongshim Construction say?

851
00:43:32,452 --> 00:43:33,652
Do they want you to leave?

852
00:43:34,552 --> 00:43:35,762
I'm sure that's what they said.

853
00:43:36,452 --> 00:43:38,292
That's how it was like when I was there.

854
00:43:38,952 --> 00:43:40,052
So what?

855
00:43:41,222 --> 00:43:42,292
Are you telling me...

856
00:43:42,322 --> 00:43:44,052
to give up if I don't want to end up like my dad?

857
00:43:47,922 --> 00:43:49,652
Leave if that's all you have to say.

858
00:44:14,822 --> 00:44:16,552
Hi, Tae Soo.

859
00:44:16,652 --> 00:44:18,922
Why are you coming out from that room?

860
00:44:18,952 --> 00:44:20,552
You should go in.

861
00:44:20,652 --> 00:44:21,922
Eun Ok's sick.

862
00:44:22,452 --> 00:44:23,552
What?

863
00:44:25,552 --> 00:44:26,552
Honey.

864
00:44:28,322 --> 00:44:30,292
What's wrong?

865
00:44:31,922 --> 00:44:33,652
You're burning up.

866
00:44:33,652 --> 00:44:34,952
Get up, let's go to the hospital.

867
00:44:35,052 --> 00:44:36,652
Goodness. There's no need for that.

868
00:44:37,192 --> 00:44:39,352
I took some pills and I feel fine now.

869
00:44:39,952 --> 00:44:41,052
The fever's coming down.

870
00:44:44,152 --> 00:44:45,552
You need to rest at home for a few days.

871
00:44:45,922 --> 00:44:48,122
What are you talking about? What about our business?

872
00:44:48,192 --> 00:44:49,922
You need a break.

873
00:44:49,952 --> 00:44:52,122
I can work with Sung Koo.

874
00:44:52,192 --> 00:44:53,322
We have your sister, too.

875
00:44:53,752 --> 00:44:54,952
Don't say that.

876
00:44:55,052 --> 00:44:56,952
I can't let my will be broken.

877
00:44:57,152 --> 00:44:59,292
I sure there will be many more days like this.

878
00:44:59,322 --> 00:45:01,322
How can I take a break every time?

879
00:45:02,022 --> 00:45:03,922
You're so stubborn.

880
00:45:06,552 --> 00:45:09,222
I feel so much better after seeing my handsome husband.

881
00:45:11,422 --> 00:45:12,422
Honey.

882
00:45:12,752 --> 00:45:14,652
Thank you for working so hard.

883
00:45:15,292 --> 00:45:17,322
I feel like you've finally got on the right track.

884
00:45:17,452 --> 00:45:19,322
It puts me at ease.

885
00:45:19,952 --> 00:45:21,352
Although I'm physically tired,

886
00:45:21,452 --> 00:45:23,452
I can sleep well.

887
00:45:24,822 --> 00:45:26,552
Then, why are you sick?

888
00:45:28,652 --> 00:45:29,852
Go to bed.

889
00:45:30,422 --> 00:45:33,652
You have to get well for you to work again.

890
00:45:33,922 --> 00:45:35,322
You need to sleep, too.

891
00:45:35,422 --> 00:45:37,022
Let's go out early tomorrow.

892
00:45:37,052 --> 00:45:39,022
I went out early today,

893
00:45:39,052 --> 00:45:40,452
and it seemed like there were...

894
00:45:40,552 --> 00:45:42,922
a lot of people passing our food truck on their way to work.

895
00:45:43,452 --> 00:45:45,422
Let's try to get more customers in the morning.

896
00:45:46,022 --> 00:45:47,652
Okay, let's do that.

897
00:45:48,322 --> 00:45:49,422
Go to bed.

898
00:46:30,192 --> 00:46:32,852
(Please allow me to get through the day.)

899
00:46:34,852 --> 00:46:38,252
We know that you are the head of the gangsters at Choongshim.

900
00:46:38,322 --> 00:46:40,152
There must be a misunderstanding.

901
00:46:40,222 --> 00:46:42,322
My husband has nothing to do with them any more.

902
00:46:42,422 --> 00:46:45,422
I don't want you to get involved with Choongshim from now on.

903
00:46:46,852 --> 00:46:48,652
Thinking about what they made us go through,

904
00:46:48,852 --> 00:46:50,552
makes me shudder.

905
00:46:51,352 --> 00:46:52,392
Okay?

906
00:46:52,452 --> 00:46:54,822
After what happened to our store, he fell ill from the shock.

907
00:46:54,922 --> 00:46:56,122
You gangsters...

908
00:46:56,252 --> 00:46:58,192
broke my family apart.

909
00:46:58,252 --> 00:46:59,552
Let me make myself clear.

910
00:46:59,952 --> 00:47:02,052
I won't let you do that to me again.

911
00:47:19,052 --> 00:47:21,922
Gosh, it's so cold.

912
00:47:21,952 --> 00:47:23,322
And there are no customers.

913
00:47:23,552 --> 00:47:26,552
That's weird, I thought we would have more business.

914
00:47:27,422 --> 00:47:28,652
How are you feeling?

915
00:47:29,692 --> 00:47:30,922
You still have the chills, don't you?

916
00:47:31,852 --> 00:47:33,152
It's not that bad.

917
00:47:33,322 --> 00:47:35,392
We still have time until lunch.

918
00:47:35,452 --> 00:47:37,252
Go get some rest.

919
00:47:37,552 --> 00:47:39,152
No, it'd be a waste of time.

920
00:47:41,422 --> 00:47:42,952
Then stay here.

921
00:47:43,322 --> 00:47:44,952
I'll go get you some honey tea.

922
00:47:46,352 --> 00:47:47,352
Thank you.

923
00:48:10,422 --> 00:48:11,552
Get out of the way.

924
00:48:11,652 --> 00:48:14,452
You still don't get it, do you?

925
00:48:15,822 --> 00:48:16,952
What are you doing?

926
00:48:17,452 --> 00:48:20,852
Why are you still in business?

927
00:48:21,122 --> 00:48:23,222
You should leave since you received compensation.

928
00:48:23,322 --> 00:48:26,052
I told you, we need proper compensation.

929
00:48:26,152 --> 00:48:28,052
Look at this punk...

930
00:48:28,152 --> 00:48:29,822
talk back at me.

931
00:48:30,392 --> 00:48:32,422
Are you trying to play us...

932
00:48:32,952 --> 00:48:34,452
to get more money out of it?

933
00:48:34,452 --> 00:48:36,552
I don't know what your talking about.

934
00:48:36,652 --> 00:48:39,422
- You little... - Don't you dare touch him.

935
00:48:39,452 --> 00:48:40,752
I'll call the police.

936
00:48:40,822 --> 00:48:43,452
Please, call the police for us.

937
00:48:43,552 --> 00:48:46,022
Let's ask them who's here illegally.

938
00:48:46,052 --> 00:48:48,522
We don't have any reason to budge until our case has been tried.

939
00:48:48,752 --> 00:48:51,022
Our attorney told us that we can win this case.

940
00:48:51,152 --> 00:48:54,352
I was going to do this peacefully,

941
00:48:54,422 --> 00:48:56,422
but if you're going to be like this, we can't help you.

942
00:48:56,852 --> 00:48:58,292
Shall we start?

943
00:48:58,422 --> 00:48:59,922
- Boys. - Yes.

944
00:49:04,422 --> 00:49:05,452
Stop it!

945
00:49:07,022 --> 00:49:09,322
Hey! Stop it now!

946
00:49:14,952 --> 00:49:16,422
Beob Kyu, what do you think you're doing?

947
00:49:17,422 --> 00:49:18,652
Seriously.

948
00:49:20,122 --> 00:49:22,922
It's none of your business. Stay out of it.

949
00:49:22,952 --> 00:49:24,222
We're doing business right now.

950
00:49:24,492 --> 00:49:27,652
You have no right to be involved in any matters related to Choongshim!

951
00:49:27,852 --> 00:49:29,222
If that's the case, do it right.

952
00:49:30,122 --> 00:49:31,852
Stop bothering innocent people.

953
00:49:34,452 --> 00:49:37,052
You can't do this, Tae Soo.

954
00:49:37,122 --> 00:49:39,152
You think you can do whatever you want because you've left Choongshim?

955
00:49:39,222 --> 00:49:41,752
I don't want to deal with you any more. Just leave.

956
00:49:41,852 --> 00:49:44,392
- Tae Soo! - Leave! Are you deaf?

957
00:49:50,952 --> 00:49:54,022
Fine. I can come back another day.

958
00:49:55,152 --> 00:49:56,752
- Let's go! - Yes, Sir.

959
00:49:57,652 --> 00:49:59,952
We'll see you later, okay?

960
00:50:01,322 --> 00:50:04,222
If you move out before that, it'd be better for all of us!

961
00:50:18,852 --> 00:50:19,852
Are you okay?

962
00:50:20,952 --> 00:50:23,392
You have to be careful in situations like this.

963
00:50:24,452 --> 00:50:26,322
I know that you're angry, but your safety is more important.

964
00:50:28,752 --> 00:50:31,652
I'm moving my food truck. I came to say goodbye.

965
00:50:32,052 --> 00:50:33,552
I hope that the misunderstanding can be cleared up.

966
00:50:37,422 --> 00:50:38,522
Keep your chin up.

967
00:50:39,852 --> 00:50:41,422
I don't know what to tell you.

968
00:50:45,652 --> 00:50:46,952
Did you plot this with them?

969
00:50:47,022 --> 00:50:50,422
Are you playing good cop bad cop?

970
00:50:57,552 --> 00:51:01,422
All I can say is that I'm sorry.

971
00:51:01,922 --> 00:51:03,222
What do you mean there's nothing you can do?

972
00:51:04,022 --> 00:51:05,452
You can help us.

973
00:51:08,822 --> 00:51:11,452
What's wrong with you? You're asking a gangster to help us?

974
00:51:13,222 --> 00:51:16,822
You held a high position when you were at Choongshim, right?

975
00:51:17,452 --> 00:51:19,022
Then you should be able to help us.

976
00:51:33,022 --> 00:51:34,122
No.

977
00:51:35,322 --> 00:51:36,652
My husband doesn't do that any more.

978
00:51:37,292 --> 00:51:38,922
He has nothing to do with Choongshim.

979
00:51:39,152 --> 00:51:40,152
Honey.

980
00:51:41,222 --> 00:51:42,322
Tell them.

981
00:51:42,752 --> 00:51:44,652
You promised me to never get involved with Choongshim again.

982
00:52:00,252 --> 00:52:01,252
I'm...

983
00:52:02,052 --> 00:52:03,192
I'm sorry.

984
00:52:04,192 --> 00:52:06,022
I'm not in a position to help you.

985
00:52:07,752 --> 00:52:10,022
Everyone, I'm so sorry.

986
00:52:13,652 --> 00:52:15,322
I hate to say this to you,

987
00:52:16,822 --> 00:52:18,392
but you won't be able to win this battle.

988
00:52:19,652 --> 00:52:20,852
End it here.

989
00:52:21,922 --> 00:52:23,552
I don't want you to get hurt.

990
00:52:24,052 --> 00:52:25,152
No.

991
00:52:27,422 --> 00:52:30,222
Whether you help me or not, I will fight Choongshim.

992
00:52:32,322 --> 00:52:33,422
I can't back off now.

993
00:52:36,852 --> 00:52:39,322
Let's go. We should to back to our food truck now.

994
00:52:40,222 --> 00:52:41,222
Hurry up.

995
00:52:53,752 --> 00:52:56,222
What? Tae Soo got involved?

996
00:52:56,322 --> 00:52:58,852
Why would Tae Soo get involved in this?

997
00:52:59,452 --> 00:53:01,652
Well... I don't really know.

998
00:53:02,452 --> 00:53:04,592
Anyway, because of Tae Soo,

999
00:53:04,952 --> 00:53:07,122
those jerks at Manbok Shophouse think they can win.

1000
00:53:09,652 --> 00:53:12,922
He makes my life difficult even after leaving Choongshim.

1001
00:53:14,222 --> 00:53:17,922
Well, shouldn't we do something about it?

1002
00:53:20,452 --> 00:53:21,452
You're right.

1003
00:53:24,222 --> 00:53:25,922
Write your name and sign at the bottom.

1004
00:53:27,422 --> 00:53:28,422
What is this?

1005
00:53:28,522 --> 00:53:30,322
(I, Yoon Tae Soo, will never get involved with Choongshim.)

1006
00:53:30,422 --> 00:53:31,422
Goodness.

1007
00:53:32,122 --> 00:53:35,552
Is this a joke? Are you seriously asking me to sign this?

1008
00:53:35,922 --> 00:53:38,752
I'm doing this because I can't trust you.

1009
00:53:39,122 --> 00:53:42,252
Sign it. And report to me even when you go to the bathroom.

1010
00:53:42,452 --> 00:53:45,222
I couldn't just walk by, so I said a few things. That's all.

1011
00:53:45,652 --> 00:53:48,652
It was a good chance to clear up the misunderstanding with them, too.

1012
00:53:48,752 --> 00:53:51,222
Then you could've just talked to them. You made me wait and...

1013
00:53:52,352 --> 00:53:54,152
Why were you listening to them ask you for help?

1014
00:53:55,122 --> 00:53:57,652
My heart sank when I saw you hesitate.

1015
00:53:58,852 --> 00:53:59,922
This way.

1016
00:54:02,322 --> 00:54:03,752
Hey! Tae Soo!

1017
00:54:06,552 --> 00:54:07,652
Hello, Eun Ok.

1018
00:54:08,422 --> 00:54:09,952
What's this?

1019
00:54:10,552 --> 00:54:13,392
"I, Yoon Tae Soo, will never get involved with Choongshim."

1020
00:54:14,022 --> 00:54:16,122
Yes. This is great.

1021
00:54:16,692 --> 00:54:18,752
Eun Ok, I've always known that you're the wise one.

1022
00:54:20,052 --> 00:54:21,192
Why are you here?

1023
00:54:21,292 --> 00:54:23,652
I came her for the kimchi fried rice. Why else?

1024
00:54:23,952 --> 00:54:25,222
Can I get two servings?

1025
00:54:29,122 --> 00:54:30,822
Are you done for the day?

1026
00:54:31,652 --> 00:54:34,952
Why would we close up already? I'll make it for you now.

1027
00:54:35,822 --> 00:54:38,292
Thank you. That looks good.

1028
00:54:38,922 --> 00:54:40,122
Spare me a second.

1029
00:54:47,952 --> 00:54:49,022
What do you want to talk to me about?

1030
00:54:49,122 --> 00:54:50,952
Stay out of things that are none of your business.

1031
00:54:51,022 --> 00:54:53,022
Just focus on your own business.

1032
00:54:53,122 --> 00:54:54,652
Do your job properly.

1033
00:54:55,452 --> 00:54:58,752
Why can't you give them what they rightfully deserve?

1034
00:54:59,322 --> 00:55:00,922
Doing so won't hurt Choongshim at all.

1035
00:55:01,322 --> 00:55:03,452
Rather, it'll improve the company's image.

1036
00:55:05,022 --> 00:55:08,952
Tae Soo. Everyone is telling me what to do these days.

1037
00:55:09,022 --> 00:55:12,452
Dad lectures at me. Even Do Kyung and Hyun Ji tell me what to do.

1038
00:55:12,552 --> 00:55:15,022
And now, you're going to join them and lecture me?

1039
00:55:15,822 --> 00:55:18,552
Mind your own business and make fried rice.

1040
00:55:18,922 --> 00:55:21,652
People's lives were ruined because of us.

1041
00:55:21,752 --> 00:55:23,422
Have some decency and don't take them down again.

1042
00:55:23,452 --> 00:55:25,922
Stop worrying about other people. Worry about keeping your own life!

1043
00:55:26,222 --> 00:55:28,552
- Are you threatening me now? - I'm not threatening you.

1044
00:55:30,022 --> 00:55:31,122
I'm giving you a word of advice.

1045
00:55:31,652 --> 00:55:33,552
Anyway, this is the last advice I'll be giving you.

1046
00:55:34,192 --> 00:55:35,392
You know what's next, right?

1047
00:55:36,652 --> 00:55:37,852
What if I tell you that I don't know?

1048
00:55:41,222 --> 00:55:43,222
Here's your kimchi fried rice.

1049
00:55:44,122 --> 00:55:45,852
Thanks, Eun Ok.

1050
00:55:47,122 --> 00:55:48,322
You should go.

1051
00:55:49,322 --> 00:55:51,652
I'm sure Tae Soo understood everything you said.

1052
00:55:53,752 --> 00:55:55,452
Yes, I shall.

1053
00:55:56,292 --> 00:55:58,322
Tae Soo. I'm going now.

1054
00:55:59,452 --> 00:56:00,652
Beob Kyu, let's go!

1055
00:56:03,422 --> 00:56:05,122
Goodness.

1056
00:56:11,122 --> 00:56:14,652
Fine. I'll sign it.

1057
00:56:16,652 --> 00:56:18,922
Mr Choi. What are you talking about now?

1058
00:56:19,492 --> 00:56:22,652
What have I done to them? Why are they suing me now?

1059
00:56:22,852 --> 00:56:24,122
Gosh. This is making my blood boil.

1060
00:56:26,452 --> 00:56:27,552
I'll get back to you.

1061
00:56:30,222 --> 00:56:32,452
Are they suing you?

1062
00:56:32,452 --> 00:56:34,952
They're targeting me now because they haven't been able...

1063
00:56:35,022 --> 00:56:37,652
to get anything out of Choongshim.

1064
00:56:37,752 --> 00:56:40,452
These jerks. They have no idea what they're dealing with.

1065
00:56:40,552 --> 00:56:42,822
Ki Beom. Let's teach them a lesson.

1066
00:56:43,122 --> 00:56:45,322
We've been too easy on them.

1067
00:56:59,652 --> 00:57:00,652
Hello?

1068
00:57:02,022 --> 00:57:04,322
It's me, Chul, from Manbok Shophouse.

1069
00:57:06,422 --> 00:57:07,752
Who? Chul?

1070
00:57:09,552 --> 00:57:11,222
The gangsters from Choongshim...

1071
00:57:12,122 --> 00:57:15,222
are vandalising our store right now! Can you help us?

1072
00:57:16,822 --> 00:57:17,822
Please help us!

1073
00:57:22,292 --> 00:57:24,822
- Chul, it's... - Please help us!

1074
00:57:25,422 --> 00:57:27,392
You're the only one who can help us.

1075
00:57:28,222 --> 00:57:30,922
- Stop it! - Move out of the way.

1076
00:57:33,452 --> 00:57:34,452
Chul. Chul!

1077
00:57:38,652 --> 00:57:40,922
What's going on? Manbok Shophouse?

1078
00:57:41,452 --> 00:57:43,122
- They called you? - Yes.

1079
00:57:44,122 --> 00:57:45,922
I think Choongshim sent some guys.

1080
00:57:46,922 --> 00:57:49,652
That boy is Sung Min's age. He was probably staying up all night to...

1081
00:57:50,322 --> 00:57:51,752
protect his shop.

1082
00:57:52,452 --> 00:57:55,452
So? Are you going to run over there?

1083
00:57:58,852 --> 00:57:59,852
Gosh.

1084
00:58:01,222 --> 00:58:02,322
Are you?

1085
00:58:03,222 --> 00:58:04,322
Goodness.

1086
00:58:08,422 --> 00:58:09,422
Well...

1087
00:58:10,752 --> 00:58:12,852
I promised you I wouldn't.

1088
00:58:13,852 --> 00:58:14,922
I'm not going.

1089
00:58:18,652 --> 00:58:19,652
Go back to sleep now.

1090
00:58:22,952 --> 00:58:26,392
- Honey. - I'm not going.

1091
00:58:32,122 --> 00:58:34,122
I'm getting myself a glass of water.

1092
00:58:35,552 --> 00:58:36,552
Go back to sleep.

1093
00:59:45,552 --> 00:59:47,022
Get off of him.

1094
00:59:47,652 --> 00:59:50,222
You're the boss here, right?

1095
00:59:50,292 --> 00:59:51,852
Please make them stop!

1096
00:59:51,952 --> 00:59:53,352
You don't remember me, do you?

1097
00:59:53,752 --> 00:59:55,852
I won't let you do that to me again.

1098
00:59:55,952 --> 00:59:57,352
You can help us.

1099
00:59:57,452 --> 00:59:59,822
You held a high position when you were at Choongshim, right?

1100
01:00:00,052 --> 01:00:01,352
Then you should be able to help us.

1101
01:00:03,822 --> 01:00:05,352
Can you help us?

1102
01:00:06,652 --> 01:00:07,922
Please help us.

1103
01:00:08,052 --> 01:00:09,952
You're the only one who can help us.

1104
01:00:17,252 --> 01:00:20,052
I don't want you to get involved with Choongshim from now on.

1105
01:00:20,922 --> 01:00:22,552
Thinking about what they made us go through,

1106
01:00:22,822 --> 01:00:24,552
makes me shudder.

1107
01:00:25,252 --> 01:00:26,292
Honey.

1108
01:00:26,822 --> 01:00:28,522
Thank you for working so hard.

1109
01:00:29,652 --> 01:00:31,652
I feel like you've finally got on the right track.

1110
01:00:31,922 --> 01:00:33,392
It puts me at ease.

1111
01:00:34,352 --> 01:00:35,692
Although I'm physically tired,

1112
01:00:35,952 --> 01:00:37,752
I can sleep well.

1113
01:00:38,352 --> 01:00:39,392
No.

1114
01:00:40,752 --> 01:00:42,392
My husband doesn't do that any more.

1115
01:00:42,452 --> 01:00:44,252
He has nothing to do with Choongshim.

1116
01:00:44,352 --> 01:00:46,052
Write your name and sign at the bottom.

1117
01:00:46,152 --> 01:00:47,752
Why were you listening to them ask you for help?

1118
01:00:48,922 --> 01:00:51,552
My heart sank when I saw you hesitate.

1119
01:01:07,652 --> 01:01:08,652
Go.

1120
01:01:24,392 --> 01:01:26,352
I must have been destined to be...

1121
01:01:26,652 --> 01:01:28,352
a wife of a gangster.

1122
01:01:31,022 --> 01:01:33,052
I thought 18 years was enough.

1123
01:01:34,392 --> 01:01:36,192
I wanted to live like a normal person.

1124
01:01:38,452 --> 01:01:40,252
But I guess it's not in the stars for me.

1125
01:01:44,752 --> 01:01:46,352
I won't be able to stop if I go now.

1126
01:01:47,822 --> 01:01:49,052
I'll have to help them until the end.

1127
01:01:51,822 --> 01:01:53,552
You think I don't know that?

1128
01:01:58,122 --> 01:01:59,152
Go.

1129
01:02:00,652 --> 01:02:02,152
Go save the country or go save a man.

1130
01:02:03,122 --> 01:02:04,452
Do whatever you want.

1131
01:02:06,392 --> 01:02:08,222
- Honey. - Go!

1132
01:02:09,292 --> 01:02:11,052
Go before I change my mind.

1133
01:02:50,152 --> 01:02:52,152
(Sweet and Scary Family)

1134
01:02:52,752 --> 01:02:54,022
You'll be going behind bars.

1135
01:02:54,052 --> 01:02:55,552
Drop the lawsuit against Manbok Shophouse.

1136
01:02:56,052 --> 01:02:57,952
Did you stick your nose in someone else's business?

1137
01:02:58,052 --> 01:02:59,552
Will it get you in trouble?

1138
01:02:59,552 --> 01:03:00,852
You're not living this life alone.

1139
01:03:00,922 --> 01:03:02,652
You need to look around and help others.

1140
01:03:02,752 --> 01:03:05,552
Mr Park called and said that he's going to quit.

1141
01:03:05,652 --> 01:03:06,922
How can you fight without a lawyer?

1142
01:03:07,122 --> 01:03:08,922
If you want to win, you need to toughen up.

1143
01:03:08,952 --> 01:03:10,322
We will lose if we don't unite.

1144
01:03:10,452 --> 01:03:12,152
You need to question me at the police station?

1145
01:03:12,222 --> 01:03:13,652
You don't have to be someone I'm proud of.

1146
01:03:13,752 --> 01:03:15,152
But don't be the person I am ashamed of.

1147
01:03:15,222 --> 01:03:17,922
Mum, let's move back to our old house.

1148
01:03:18,052 --> 01:03:19,222
For the last three years,

1149
01:03:19,292 --> 01:03:21,022
I was really happy...

1150
01:03:21,052 --> 01:03:22,452
and thankful.

1151
01:03:22,552 --> 01:03:24,452
Just let me go.

1152
01:03:25,292 --> 01:03:27,452
Why are you waiting for someone that's not going to come?

1153
01:03:27,552 --> 01:03:30,052
We have to leave this place if we want to live.

1154
01:03:30,352 --> 01:03:32,552
Attacking them first can be our best defence.

1155
01:03:32,652 --> 01:03:33,652
I apologise.

1156
01:03:33,752 --> 01:03:36,192
I calculated the compensation,

1157
01:03:36,352 --> 01:03:38,552
and it turns out you should be getting twice the amount.

1158
01:03:38,652 --> 01:03:41,352
We want you out of this.

1159
01:03:41,452 --> 01:03:44,192
With money and power, you can do anything.

1160
01:03:44,252 --> 01:03:45,552
Boss!

1161
01:04:15,752 --> 01:04:17,452
the Family Court is always full.

1162
01:04:17,552 --> 01:04:18,652
(Go Dong Mi, never had a boyfriend)

1163
01:04:18,752 --> 01:04:22,322
You should be suspicious. Reasonable suspicion is important.

1164
01:04:22,352 --> 01:04:23,352
(Baek Da Jeong, soon to be divorced)

1165
01:04:23,852 --> 01:04:26,552
Bring me the big ones. As big as melons!

1166
01:04:26,652 --> 01:04:27,652
(Hong Ae Ran, soon to be married)

1167
01:04:27,852 --> 01:04:29,952
(A romantic comedy with a cheerful energy)

1168
01:04:30,192 --> 01:04:32,952
(Happy Ending Once Again)

